Name: Every Flavor Bell-less Crab
AttributesDescription: Increases all team members' ATK by 22% and Crit. DMG by 24% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: Bell Crabs shed their iconic bells during certain times of the year. During this period, these crabs are also known as "Bell-less Crabs," said to have a distinct flavor apart from Bell Crabs.
